  "text": "T. brucei infections in mice have been shown to compromise host humoral immune competence and to induce the loss of specific mature B cell populations in the spleen [CITATION_1] . However, little is known about how B lymphopoiesis in the bone marrow is affected during T. brucei infection. Here, B lymphopoiesis has been examined using a C57BL/6 mouse T. brucei AnTat 1.1E infection",
